    "English": "Autonomous Control Unit",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "自主控制单元",
    "TraditionalChinese": "自主控制單位"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A semi-autonomous <span class=\"name name-technology\">artificial pilot plugin</span> for the Minotaur Heavy Exocraft Hybrid. Installation allows the Minotaur to <span class=\"name name-stellar\">traverse planets itself</span> and engage in <span class=\"name name-stellar\">combat</span> or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">mining</span> activities to support its primary operator.<br><br>The AI pilot will always cede control to the primary operator when they enter the cockpit.<br><br>Piloting routines are highly localised. It is incapable of developing emotional bonds nor exercising independent control of the Minotaur.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专为弥诺陶洛斯重型混合强化艇设计的半自主<span class=\"name name-technology\">智能导航插件</span>。安装后，弥诺陶洛斯将能够<span class=\"name name-stellar\">独立跨越行星</span>并与敌人<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交战</span>，除此以外还能进行<span class=\"name name-stellar\">采矿</span>以帮助自己的主要操作员。<br><br>当主要操作员进入驾驶舱后，人工智能驾驶员将移交设备控制权。<br><br>导航程序已经过高度本地化。人工智能无法与操作员产生情感联系，也无法完全独立操纵弥诺陶洛斯。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種半自主<span class=\"name name-technology\">人工駕駛員外掛程式</span>，用於彌諾陶洛斯重型混合強化艇。安裝後能讓彌諾陶洛斯<span class=\"name name-stellar\">獨自穿越星球</span>並進行<span class=\"name name-stellar\">戰鬥</span>或者<span class=\"name name-stellar\">採礦</span>活動，以支援其主要操作員。<br><br>主要操作員進入駕駛艙後，人工駕駛員將會交付控制權。<br><br>飛行程序高度在地化。無法發展出情感連結，也無法自由控制彌諾陶洛斯。"
  },
